# hello_world

## Project overview
A single-file Python/Flask REST API with three endpoints (/, /health, /greet/<name>) that serves as a minimal greeting and health-check service.

## Language and framework
- Primary language: Python
- Framework: Flask
- Build system: pip

## Critical commands
- Install: pip install -r requirements.txt
- Build: pip install -r requirements.txt
- Test: pytest
- Run locally: Not determinable from source

